OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,FRob Smith reports from Ashton-under-
OL,7,FLyne
OL,9,FA man whose remains were found
OL,10,Fscattered around areas of Salford has
OL,11,Fbeen named as 67-year-old Stuart
OL,12,FEverett.
OL,14,FPolice say the formal identification
OL,15,Fprocess is yet to take place but DNA
OL,16,Fsamples have been sent away for urgent
OL,17,Fforensic analysis
OL,19,FHowever, their specially trained
OL,20,Fofficers are now supporting Stuart's
OL,21,Ffamily.
