OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,FHis torso and other body parts were
OL,7,Ffirst discovered in Kersal wetlands in
OL,8,FSalford on April 4.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, two men appeared at
OL,11,FManchester Crown Court charged with
OL,12,Fhis murder.
OL,14,FMichal Jaroslaw Polchowski and Marcin
OL,15,FMajerkiewicz, both of Worsley Road,
OL,16,FEccles, were remanded in custody.
OL,18,FA provisional trial date of March 3
OL,19,Fnext year was fixed by Judge Nicholas
OL,20,FDean KC, the Honorary Recorder of
OL,21,FManchester.
