OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,FPolice say the remains found at three
OL,7,Fother locations in Salford are still
OL,8,Fto be tested, but they are confident
OL,9,Fthey belong to the same victim.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Lewis Hughes
OL,12,Ffrom GMP's Serious Crime Division,
OL,13,Fsaid: "My thoughts and the thoughts of
OL,14,Fofficers and staff across Greater
OL,15,FManchester Police are with Stuart's
OL,16,Ffamily at this traumatic time. Family
OL,17,FLiaison Officers are supporting them
OL,18,Fthrough each update in our
OL,19,Finvestigation.
