OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,F"On behalf of Stuart's loved ones, I
OL,7,Fask the public and the press to please
OL,8,Frespect their wishes for peace and
OL,9,Fprivacy while they process this most
OL,10,Fdevastating news.
OL,12,F"My officers and detectives, alongside
OL,13,Fadditional resources from across the
OL,14,Fforce, have worked tirelessly over the
OL,15,Flast three days to secure charges.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
