OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,F"We are grateful for the public's
OL,7,Fcontinued help and support throughout
OL,8,Fthis case. We understand the
OL,9,Fshockwaves this has caused throughout
OL,10,Fthe community and beyond, and we hope
OL,11,Fyou are reassured by the pace of our
OL,12,Finvestigation and also our large
OL,13,Fpolice presence in the areas as we
OL,14,Fcontinue to make enquiries.
OL,16,F"We have officers drawn from different
OL,17,Fteams and units in GMP who have helped
OL,18,Fus search and their efforts do not go
OL,19,Funnoticed, and they have all played an
OL,20,Fimportant role to help us get to this
OL,21,Fstage in our investigation.
