OL,3,CSalford torso investigation: Victim
OL,4,Cnamed as 67-year-old Stuart Everett
OL,6,F"We said right at the start that our
OL,7,Finvestigation will not stop until we
OL,8,Fhave every stone unturned, and this
OL,9,Fcontinues to be the case. Our
OL,10,Finvestigation has been a huge process
OL,11,Fso far, and we will continue to push
OL,12,Fforward in our enquiries to find
OL,13,Fanswers for Stuart's family."
